title: 11 Maths Puzzle Books (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 11 books on mathematical problems & puzzles in PDF format:

01. 100 Great Problems of Elementary Mathematics - Their History and Solution
02. Five Hundred Mathematical Challenges
03. Mathematical Circus by Martin Gardner
04. Mathematical Mysteries - The Beauty and Magic of Numbers1
05. Mathematical Quickies - 270 Stimulating Problems with Solutions
06. New Mathematical Diversions - More Puzzles, Problems, Games, & Other Mathematical Diversions
07. One Hundred Problems in Elementary Mathematics
08. The Magic of Numbers by Eric Tenple Bell
09. Vision in Elementary Mathematics by W.W. Sawyer
10. The Liar Paradox and the Towers of Hanoi - The Ten Greatest Math Puzzles of All Time
11. Great Book of Math Puzzles by Philip Heafford
